data.title: Music Maker Co-Founder Tim Duffy spoke with Paul Foster of WNCW on Music Maker’s 30 years of advocating for under-resourced roots...
data.meta_description:
50 likes, 0 comments - musicmakerfdn on March 4, 2024: "Music Maker Co-Founder Tim Duffy spoke with Paul Foster of WNCW on Music Maker’s 30 years of advocating for under-resourced roots musicians, and how Song Keepers captures these efforts.

Photos:
1. Albert Smith, Drink Small. Rembart, SC. 1998. T. Duffy.
2. Benton Flippen, Hillsborough, NC 2003. T. Duffy.
3. Cary Morin. Hillsborough, NC, 2017. T Duffy.
4. Bishop Dready Manning, Roanoke Rapids, NC. 2005. T. Duffy.
5. Faith & Harmony. Fountain, NC. 2020. A. Greenhood.
6. David Butler. Hillsborough, NC, 2002. T Duffy.
7. Church Piano, Uchee, AL. 2019. T. Duffy.
8. Cora Mae Bryant. Covington, GA, 1997. D. Bryant.
9. Cover of Song Keepers! Get yourself a copy at the link in our bio.

#musicmakerfdn #songkeepers #roots #blues #bluegrass #americana".
